org.dellroad.stuff.xml

Class StreamWriterDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dellroad.stuff.xml.StreamWriterDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XMLStreamWriter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotatedXMLStreamWriter, EmptyTagXMLStreamWriter, IndentXMLStreamWriter

    public class StreamWriterDelegate
extends Object
implements XMLStreamWriter
    Support superclass for filtering XMLStreamWriter implementations. All methods delegate to the configured parent.
